## How to Use These Files

### Option 1: Keep Interactive Simulator (Current)
Your current `App.js` is the interactive simulator. Use the **Complete App.css** I provided.

**Steps:**
1. Replace your `src/App.css` with the "Complete App.css with Simulator Styles"
2. Replace `src/App.test.js` with the "Updated App.test.js"
3. Replace `src/tests/App.test.js` with the updated tests file
4. Run `npm test` to verify all tests pass

### Option 2: Use Simple Deployed Version
If you want the simple static display page (as shown in README screenshot):

**Steps:**
1. Replace `src/App.js` with "Simple Deployed App.js (Alternative)"
2. Replace `src/App.css` with "Simple Deployed App.css (Alternative)"
3. Update `src/App.test.js` with simpler tests for the static version

